data.description: Embrace suburban serenity in this 3-bed, 2-bath Edmond home on a generous 1.24 acres. Upgraded with a roof, and HVAC system just over a year ago. It also features a recently added storm shelter and hot water heater for peace of mind. The expansive yard calls for outdoor enjoyment or custom landscaping. Sunlight floods the welcoming interior, highlighting the open living spaces and a private en-suite in the master bedroom with a walk-in closet. This home also offers an extra room right off the entrance that could be utilized for office space or a playroom. The efficient layout connects to a kitchen perfect for gatherings. Enjoy the two covered patios overlooking the spacious backyard, a setting for all seasons. The home blends modern amenities with the charm of country living, a perfect canvas to create your home sanctuary.
